extendedInfo.description: If you are looking for an Android tool to save your tax, this is for you.Feature List:- Keep track your income.- Keep track every tax deductible items (expense, mileage, entertainment...). - Calculate your tax and tax savings based on the Official 2011 US Income Tax Brackets (IRS Tax Rates).- Send the reports to your Tax Preparer at the end of the year if you like.- Edit or delete a missing item.- Search items by full-text-search or filters.* Keywords: tax saving, tax calculator, income manager, expense manager, tax manager, tax brackets, tax report, finance, finance manager, personal finance, personal finance manager
